title: Wednesday Post Show (06-01-22)

description:
Bobby starts talking about how the price of gas is really hurting people right now. He gets to stories about a woman marrying a plane and a guy whose life was ruined by the lottery. Bobby and Lunchbox get into the topic of parallel universe. Raymundo gives an update on country music secrets.
